    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The high-revving power plant delivers linear torque and an 8,400 RPM crescendo. This example maintains its mechanical integrity with a focus on core performance components; the M Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional lateral traction, while the suspension geometry remains tight and responsive. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rod bearings and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and induction systems operate at peak efficiency. While showing signs of honest use consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the chassis remains stiff and the hydraulic steering rack offers the communicative feedback modern EPS systems lack. A driver-focused machine ready for the canyons.",
