    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior remains striking with a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather seats show only light bolstering wear on the driver's side, and the dashboard is free of any cracks or sun damage. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes were serviced just last season. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that has been garage-kept and smoke-free. It offers the premium experience of a high-end model without the 'new car' price tag. Included are two sets of keys and a thick folder of service receipts.",
